---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
const pageTitle = "Posts";
---
<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonLaptopGif" src="/blog.webp"/>
    </div>

    <h2>Research Publications</h2>
    <ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
        <Card
            href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2310.12357"
            image="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/7a/ArXiv_logo_2022.png"
            title="Large Language Models for Code Analysis: Do LLMs Really Do Their Job?"
            body={`Large language models (LLMs) have demonstrated significant potential in natural language understanding and programming code processing tasks. This paper offers a comprehensive evaluation of LLMs' effectiveness in code analysis, particularly in the context of obfuscated code. Through a series of Institutional Review Board (IRB)-approved real-world tests, our AI-enabled spear phishing framework achieved varying success rates, highlighting both the capabilities and limitations of LLMs in enhancing and scaling phishing attacks. We also discuss ethical considerations, limitations, and defense strategies to guard against such malicious uses of AI.`}
        />
    </ul>

    <h2>Additional Research</h2>
    <ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
        <Card
            href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1HeLqe2Jz8U7XHVQLe5XEynzRTHioYgQS/view?usp=sharing"
            image="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/7a/ArXiv_logo_2022.png"
            title="Enhancing Spear-Phishing Attacks with AI"
            body={`Exploring the intersection of AI and cybersecurity, this paper presents a case study on leveraging machine learning and LLMs to scale spear-phishing attacks. Through an AI-enabled attack generation framework, we conducted real-world tests demonstrating the viability of advanced phishing strategies. The study also delves into ethical considerations and proposes defense mechanisms to mitigate such AI-driven threats.`}
        />
    </ul>

    <h2>Blog</h2>
    <ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
        <Card
            href="https://medium.com/@ssrivastav_46455/unveiling-the-mathematics-behind-transformer-models-shaurya-srivastav-2fe1e47d20f9"
            image="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1200/0*FSZ330S1hKorTBOn.png"
            title="Mathematics Behind Transformer Models | Views: 2.2K Reads: 1.1k"
            body="Unravel the mathematical intricacies powering Transformer models, the driving force behind modern natural language processing breakthroughs."
        />
        <Card
            href="https://medium.com/@ssrivastav_46455/adversarial-attacks-on-nlp-models-guarding-against-trojan-threats-shaurya-srivastav-4c1966677d36"
            image="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1200/0*FSZ330S1hKorTBOn.png"
            title="Adversarial Attacks on NLP Models"
            body="Unlock the cryptic world of adversarial machine learning, where Trojan attacks secretly infiltrate AI NLP models, and discover the technical strategies to defend against these hidden threats."
        />
        <Card
            href="https://medium.com/@ssrivastav_46455/demystifying-common-data-structures-arrays-linked-lists-stacks-and-queues-part-i-148f0c4bb781"
            image="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1200/0*FSZ330S1hKorTBOn.png"
            title="Demystifying Common Data Structures: Arrays, Linked Lists, Stacks, and Queues (Part I)"
            body="Unlock the secrets of efficient coding by exploring common data structures through the delicious lens of cooking."
        />
    </ul>

