        Feel free to reach out through <a href="mailto:ssrivastav@ucdavis.edu">email</a> or connect with me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/shauryasrivastav/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>.
